DeathSteel::

He smiled and folded his arms over his chest. "Ah, yess, the old 
homestead. I had almost forgotten it. What are we to do? Cast our 
shadow on the planet and have it fall to us? Oh yess, I wish to see 
that very thing happen." he said with an evil grin on his face.
